    "content": "Tabbed by: bassm99\r\nE-mail: alanmatthews1966@yahoo.co.uk\r\n\r\nTuning: E, A, D, G\r\n\r\n\"Dress You Up\" from the album \"Like A Virgin\" (1984)\r\nWritten by Peggy Stanziale/Andrea LaRusso\r\n\r\nBass Starts: 0:02\r\n\r\nIntro: (Play 3 Times)\r\n \r\n[tab]G|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nE|--4-4-4-4-4-4-4-4--4-4-4-4-4-4-4-4--6-6-6-6-6-6-6-6--6-6-6-6-6-6-6-6------|[/tab]\r\n\r\nVerse:\r\n\r\n[tab]G|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nE|--4-4-4-4-4-4-4-4--4-4-4-4-4-4-4-4--6-6-6-6-6-6-6-6--6-6-6-6-6-6-6-6-(x3)-|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nE|--1-1-1-1-1-1-1-3--4-4-4-4-4-4-4-4--3-3-3-3-3-3-3-3--3-3-3-3-3-3-3-3-(x1)-|[/tab]\r\n\r\nChorus: (Play 4 Times)\r\n\r\n[tab]G|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|----------------------------3-5-6-3---------------------------------------|\r\nE|--4-4-4-4--6-6-6-6--3-3-3-3-----------------------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\nRepeat Verse:\r\n\r\nRepeat Chorus: (Play 8 Times)\r\n\r\nGuitar Solo:\r\n\r\n[tab]G|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nE|--4-4-4-4-4-4-4-4--4-4-4-4-4-4-4-4--6-6-6-6-6-6-6-6--6-6-6-6-6-6-6-6-(x3)-|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nE|--1-1-1-1-1-1-1-3--4-4-4-4-4-4-4-4--3-3-3-3-3-3-3-3--3-3-3-3-3-3-3-3-(x1)-|[/tab]\r\n\r\nRepeat Chorus: (Play 26 Times To Fade) (2:30 - 4:01)",
